couk.chrisjenx.androidmaplib.overlays
Class OutOfBoundsOverlay

java.lang.Object
  Overlay
      couk.chrisjenx.androidmaplib.overlays.OutOfBoundsOverlay

public class OutOfBoundsOverlay
extends Overlay

This object is designed to listen to other events coming from the map overlays and tell you if out of bounds. It's also configurable to move you back to the bounding box.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Chris Jenkins

setAutoBounding

public void setAutoBounding(boolean autoBound,
                            boolean snap)
This disables/enables the auto bounding feature. Meaning that the overlay will try to keep you locked to bounding box.

Parameters:
autoBound - true enables autobounding
snap - true means that it will snap back to within the bounds, false will animate back
